          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="close-customgram-modal modal-close">
              <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-5">
                <ModalProjectPicture src={Customgram} alt="Customgram logo" />
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2">Customgram</h1>
                <p class="font-bold">An Unofficial Telegram client.</p>
                <div class="flex space-x-2 mt-2">
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://github.com/AmanoTeam/Customgram"
                  >
                    <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a class="project-button" href="https://t.me/Customgram">
                    <i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.telegram.customgram"
                  >
                    <i class="fab fa-google-play"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://customgram.amanoteam.com"
                  >
                    <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="project-desc">
                <p>
                  Customgram is an unofficial Telegram client with some useful
                  additions.
                </p>
                <p>Features</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Max accounts increased to 10.</li>
                  <li>Option to set up a proxy before login.</li>
                  <li>Option to clear media from cache.</li>
                  <li>"Delete for everyone" enabled by default.</li>
                  <li>Upload date for profile photos.</li>
                  <li>Links and username on user bios clickable.</li>
                </ul>
