            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-5">
                <ModalProjectPicture src={LyricsPy} alt="LyricsPy logo" />
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2">LyricsPy</h1>
                <p class="font-bold">
                  Python bot and library to search for music lyrics.
                </p>
                <div class="flex space-x-2 mt-2">
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://github.com/AmanoTeam/LyricsPy"
                  >
                    <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a
                    class="project-button"
                    href="https://pypi.org/project/lyricspy"
                  >
                    <i class="fab fa-python"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a class="project-button" href="https://t.me/LyricsPyBot">
                    <i class="fab fa-telegram-plane"></i>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="project-desc">
                <p>
                  LyricsPy is a Python bot and library created by <a
                    href="https://t.me/RianFC">Rian</a
                  > to search for music lyrics and show the current playing song
